ionservice->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend调用productcatalogservice的GetProduct接口：正常耗时11.37秒，异常耗时13.39秒，延迟增加17.8%；recommendationservice调用productcatalogservice的ListProducts接口：正常耗时74毫秒，异常耗时110.5毫秒，延迟增加49%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"frontend自身处理GetProduct请求：正常耗时11.37秒，异常耗时13.39秒，存在内部处理延迟\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析要点：**\n\n1. **主要异常模式**：productcatalogservice 出现显著延迟，特别是来自frontend的GetProduct调用延迟明显增加。\n\n2. **调用链关系**：\n   - `frontend->productcatalogservice`：GetProduct接口延迟增加\n   - `recommendationservice->productcatalogservice`：ListProducts接口延迟增加\n\n3. **根因定位**：productcatalogservice 是异常传播的源头，因为多个上游服务（frontend和recommendationservice）调用它时都出现延迟，而productcatalogservice本身没有显示更下游的依赖异常。\n\n4. **异常特征**：没有发现连接拒绝或熔断错误，主要是响应时间增加，表明是服务处理性能下降而非完全不可用。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的指标数据，我现在进行初始扫描分析。从指标数据可以看出，这是一个非常显著的故障事件，几乎所有Pod的指标在故障期间都降为0，表明发生了大规模的服务中断。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"pod_cpu_usage\", \"pod_processes\", \"pod_network_transmit_packets\", \"pod_network_receive_packets\", \"pod_memory_working_set_bytes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_processes指标从1.0降为0.0，表明Pod进程终止，同时pod_cpu_usage和网络指标也降为0\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_processes: 1.0→0.0 (变化率2.0), pod_cpu_usage: 0.0→0.0 (变化率0.0)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage从0.04降为0.0，网络传输包数从100.39降为0.0，表明Pod完全停止运行\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0.04→0.0 (变化率2.0), pod_network_transmit_packets: 100.39→0.0 (变化率2.0)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-0\", \n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage从0.06降为0.0，网络传输包数从353.89降为0.0，Pod完全失效\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0.06→0.0 (变化率2.0), pod_network_transmit_packets: 353.